snippet: Harvick dominated a race he had to win to advance to the second round of Nascar’s playoffs, while the six-time champion Jimmie Johnson was eliminated from the field.
abstract: Kevin Harvick wins at Dover International Speedway, advancing to Chase for the Sprint Cup.
lead_paragraph: Harvick dominated a race he had to win to advance to the second round of Nascar’s playoffs, while the six-time champion Jimmie Johnson was eliminated from the field.
